long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension provides a link between Facebook and Biglead, allowing Biglead users to appear on the Facebook interface.
support features:
- Display phone number on Facebook from Biglead application
- Displays information related to the user
